<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset ="UTF-8">
    <meta name ="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel ="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
    <title>insert</title>
  </head>
  <body>
  <div class="w3-top">
    <div class ="w3-var w3-dark-grey">
      <a href="/home" class="w3-bar-item-w3-button">홈</a>
      <a href="/insert" class="w3-bar-item-w3-button">추가</a>
      <a href="/edit" class="w3-bar-item-w3-button">수정</a>
      <a href="/del" class="w3-bar-item-w3-button">삭제</a>
      <a href="/list" class="w3-bar-item-w3-button">조회</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br>
  <div class="w3-header w3-center">
    <h2>회원정보추가</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="w3-table w3-cyan w3-center">
    <form action ="/insert" method = "post">
      <div class="w3-center w3-text-white"><h3>새로운 회원정보를 입력하세요</h3></div>
      <table text-ailgin="center">
        <tr>
          <td><label>회원 이름</label></td>
          <td><input type="text" name ="name" placeholder="이름"</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><label>거주지(도시)</label></td>
          <td><input type= "text" name = "region" placeholder="거주지"</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td><td><input type ="submit" value="저장" class= "w3-button w3-round xxlarge w3-khaki w3-block"</td>
        </tr>
        <tr></tr>
      </table>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class = "w3-margin w3 text-blue">
    <p>회원번호는 자동생성, 삭제된 번호에는 재배정되지 않음.</p>
  </div>
  <table class="w3-table-all">
    <thread>
      <tr class= "w3-blue">
        <th>번호</th><th>성명</th><th>거주지</th>
      </thread>
      <% data.forEach(function(user){ %>
            <tr>
              <td>[<%=user.id%>]</td>
              <td><%=user.name%></td>
              <td><%=user.region%></td>
            </tr>
            <% }) %>

      </table>
    </body>
    </html>
